automatically determine a value for a distance L, wherein the distance L is the distance between a current vehicle position and a position where the first local required speed will change to the second local required speed;
automatically determine a value for a time T which is equivalent to a value obtained by dividing the value for the distance L by the value indicative of the current vehicle speed;
automatically determine whether the current vehicle speed is less than the new set vehicle speed;
automatically receive a fourth signal indicative of a local traffic density;
automatically determine a value for a time Δt based on a predetermined relationship between Δt and traffic density;
